%% L1 to L2 Deposit Flow (SDK)
sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant L1 as L1 (LineaRollup)
    participant Coord as Coordinator
    participant L2 as L2 (L2MessageService)

    User->>L1: deposit()
    L1->>L1: MessageSent event
    L1->>Coord: Event detected
    Coord->>L2: anchor hash
    User->>L2: getL1ToL2MessageStatus()
    L2-->>User: CLAIMABLE
    User->>L2: claimOnL2()
    L2-->>User: ETH received
